Package com.engineersbox.httpproxy.resolver.annotation

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HandlerType  
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ExceptionHandler
    Describes the throwable type to handle within a given annotated method
    Handler
    Describes the type of handler a given annotated class is.
    MediaType
    Describes the RFC 2616 Section 3.7 compliant media type to handle in a given method.
    Path
    Specifies a path to be handle be a resource or method.
    PathParam
    Designates a method parameter to be filled with the matching path parameter from the handled endpoint path

    For example, with a path designated by /account/{id}/users, anything of the form /account/.*\/ will be matched and the {id} part will be passed as a String to the constructor of AccID through injection.
